id: pm-gantt-chart-gtqn
title: Add % complete (progress) rendering to Gantt bars
description: ""
type: Feature
status: open
priority: 2
tags: []
created_at: "2026-06-04T23:13:05.334Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-04T23:13:05.334Z"
author: codex
body: "Add an opt-in --progress flag that derives a per-item progress ratio from pm signals (closed/canceled=100%, in_progress=acceptance-criteria checked ratio or 50% default, open=0%) and renders it: ASCII as a trailing NN% plus partial-fill glyph, Mermaid via native 'done'/percentage tag, HTML as a fill width overlay. Default output (no flag) must remain byte-identical to keep existing tests/golden output intact."
